civics.name: Default Town Sales Tax
civics.description:
Purpose: Basic sales tax for other towns and states to copy
Type: Example Law
Author: Elmeye
Maintainer: Elmeye

Dont forget to change all the default town refrences and tax codes, you will need to update the state offices district as well.

properties.Title: Sales Tax
properties.UserDescription:
A flat tax of 5% on all sales within Default Town. An exception is made for the State Office, as well as skillless players actively selling.  It also takes into account companies.
A sales tax of 5% is the maximum amount that Towns and States can do.

properties.Title: Town Mayors Wage
properties.UserDescription:
Each hour the town mayor is paid a wage at 15% of the index wage, this might not seem alot but it will increase as the cycle progresses.
Type !indexwage to find out what that is.
This example only pays out on active to save the town treasury being drained if a Mayor stops playing.
